title: Tension as Husam gatecrashes anti-Husam ceramah
text:
More 
Speakers at a ceramah targeting Salor state assemblyperson Husam Musa last night received a rude shock when the man himself turned up uninvited and sat down beside them on the stage. 
The ceramah, held at Stadium Sultan Muhammad IV in Kota Bharu, was titled: "Husam lari dari debat baiah" (Husam runs away from debate on religious oath). 
Clad in a purple shirt, Husam strolled to the stage and sat there calmly while Keterah PAS chief Wan Ismail Wan Jusoh was speaking.
